snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP Is A VOICE For Male VICTIMS! - Ian McNicholl's Story
snippet.description:
A look at JOHNNY DEPP as A VOICE For Male  VICTIMS - Ian McNicholl's Story. Ian McNicholl was a businessman who endured so much horrendous suffering at the hands of his female partner Michelle.

In his 2 courts cases relating to ex wife amber heard Johnny Depp has given a voice to all victims but to male victims of DV in particular.
This helps to give confidence to those men who feel too ashamed to come forward. Johnny Depp is himself the victim of DV from amber heard.
